high_descs: Turn around and walk to the brown shelf next to the door.
Pick up the white mug on the shelf.
Turn right and walk to the fridge next to the blue trash can.
Chill the mug in the fridge and then pick up the mug from the fridge and close the fridge.
Turn around and then walk to the right to the brown shelf.
Place the mug on the top brown shelf.
anns.task_desc: Place a chilled mug on the top brown shelf next to the door.

high_descs: Turn to the left and go straight back the room. Turn right to face the brown shelf.
Pick up the mug from the shelf.
Carry the mug and turn to the right, then the left to find the fridge.
Open the fridge and place the mug inside, then shut the door. Open the fridge and get the mug out and shut the door.
Hold the mug and go right around the fridge, back to the shelf.
Place the mug on the shelf.
anns.task_desc: Chill a mug and place it on the shelf.

high_descs: Turn and go to the shelves by the door.
Pick up a coffee cup on the shelves.
Turn and go to the refrigerator.
Chill the coffee cup in the refrigerator
Turn and go to the shelves by the door.
Put the coffee cup on the shelves.
anns.task_desc: Chill the coffee cup on the shelves.
